      "value": "<p><strong>Frequency: </strong>Once per day</p>\n<hr />\n<p>You signal one enemy to be swiftly eliminated. Target an enemy within 60 feet of you. <br />Once per player per turn, when you and your allies deal damage to the target, you  deal additional precision damage to the target equal to your leadership dice. <br />If the target of Focus Fire dies, you can switch targets to another enemy as a single action with the command trait as well as the auditory or visual trait.<br />@UUID[Compendium.pf2e-warlord.warlord.Item.CsZ80x81t3rfdQje]<br />Focus Fire ends after 1 minute.<br />@UUID[Compendium.pf2e-warlord.warlord.Item.vZSBvNz5M9IqECZl]<br />@UUID[Compendium.pf2e-warlord.warlord.Item.iuuCr8DvZnavV8lT]</p>"
